{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260429/s00024/fcb0e9763c344e70a2caa7d03579256d.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>天文台下午4時45分發出特別天氣提示：與冷鋒相關的雷雨區正影響珠江口一帶。預料本港未來一兩小時部分地區雨勢較大。市民請提高警惕。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T09:44:09.313918+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":64,"images":1,"source":"明報 消閒","fallback":"none"}}